!commands!.what-is-discord:
**__What is Discordapp?__** 
 Discord app is a client that allows you to talk to a lot of different users at once. It allows you to communicate with several different people at once. Ever been on an IRC chat? AIM? AOL or Compuserve chat rooms? Or even Skype. Think that. It's alot easier. Anyone can set up a server, set it's region, and so forth.
 **__Why should you use Discord over?__** 
 Discordapp is based on servers. You could be in the middle of the desert or the ocean and still be able to talk to the server you're in as long as you have a stable connection to that sattelite! 
 Discordapp was originally meant for gamers all over for PC but it turned into more. It turned into people using it as the new chatroom method, making friendships and making their own personal groups! Discord has so many different uses. I suggest checking out discord.me for more groups! Even asking people in other servers what they think!

!commands!.faqs:
__**FAQs**__

Q - Can I just be here and have fun or do I have to be a creator?
A - You're more than welcome to stay! We encourage everyone to chill with us. We love new furries of all shapes and sizes, genders, creed, whatever! We don't care what you are!
Q - If I need help with a project, where can I ask it? 
A - These channels, <#901381714465656842> and <#895033362069217311> are the main 2 places to help you out! 
Q- I can't see anything what do?
A- You will need the furry tag! Ask an admin/mod for it!
Q - If I have a problem with someone, will the mods actually help?
A - **Tarra** is almost always online. Ask any mod or admin here, let them know you're from this discord and they will talk to you about it directly.
Q - I'm a teenager, am I allowed in <#900899476204572702> or <#933610078404243487> channels? 
A - Not right now, they are barred off till further notice. 
Q -Is there any way to be age verified here? Do I have to show my ID or anything? 
A - No, we wont ask for ID here because it's against Discord TOS. We are going by the honor system here. 
Q - Other servers hate it when I message admins and mods what about you guys? 
A - We want you to message us if you have a problem. We have an **Open Door Policy** here. 
Q - I'm a teenager and an adult is being sexual with me and I'm uncomfortable with it, what should I do? ||reverse the teen adult||
A - Let us know and we will see what's going on. We take these sorts of things very seriously.

**If a question you wish to ask was not answered here, post it and we will answer it! **
